Package: CardioRVAR
Type: An R package for the analysis 
Title: An R package for the analysis of closed-loop cardiovascular interactions
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alvaro Chao-Ecija
Maintainer: Alvaro Chao-Ecija
Description: This is an R package designed for modelling cardiovascular open-
             and closed-loop interactions. It is advisable that this package 
             is used with the separate ShinyApp interface, CarioRVAR Shiny,
             for a better user-friendly experience.
